# Authentication / Home Page Roadmap

## Authentication

### Sign-up Page
- **First Name**: Text Area
- **Last Name**: Text Area
- **Date of Birth**: Selector
- **Email**: Text Input
- **Password**: Text Input
- **Submit Button**: To submit new user's information and create a new account

### Log-in Page
- **Email**: Text Input
- **Password**: Text Input
- **Connect Button**: To confirm email address and password connection

## Home Page

- **Log-in Button**: A button that redirects to the Log-in page (disappears after user connects)
- **Sign-up Button**: A button that redirects to the Sign-up page (disappears after user connects)
- **Categories Bar**: A bar describing the user's category (e.g., man, woman, kid, baby)
- **Products Search Bar**: A search bar for finding products
- **Add to Cart Menu**: A menu displaying the products added to the cart
- **Favorite Products List**: A list displaying the user's favorite products (wishlist, can be developed as a separate web page)
- **Account Button**: A button that redirects to the user's Dashboard (information about the user, payment methods, etc.)
- **Product Area**: An area displaying products (new products, products on discount, favorite products)

**IMPORTANT NOTE**: There might be some modifications (additions/deletions) in terms of functionalities during the development process.

